 Many Lowvelders have questioned their recent water bills and used social media to voice their dismay about billing that they believe might be inaccurate. Lowvelder is currently investigating with Sembcorp Silulumanzi in an effort to get clarity on the concerns of consumers and will keep the reader’s up to date.         If you are under the impression that your billed amount might be wrong you can take the follow steps to address it: Take your bill to the Sembcorp Silulumanzi offices to see a dedicated customer service consutant about your account. Address: 
